beer.beer_description:
Our brand spankin’ new DIPA is the head honcho of the plains. It’s 10 pounds of crazy in a 5 pound sack! 6 shooters blazin’ with a star studded cast of Citra Cryo, Simcoe and Nelson Sauvin. Intense flavours of grapefruit, mango and mandarin – it’s the swill you want when yer fixin’ to saddle up for a rootin’ tootin’ night of ruckus.

Grab a pint, giddy up and ride ya’ll!
